snippet.title: Amber Heard and Vito Schnabel, The Actress Wears - She Confirms Romance with Heidi Klum's ex
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Vito Schnabel, The Actress Wears - She Confirms Romance with Heidi Klum's ex

Amber Heard and Vito Schnabel were first spotted together in the back seat of a dark SUV in New York City in early May.

And it looks as if the spark has just gotten stronger between the budding lovebirds.

On Tuesday the 32-year-old actress from Texas and the 31-year-old Brooklyn-born art curator look to be going strong as they were pictured holding hands while walking in New York City.

Thank you and subscribe
